Why I selected the Whitney compilation:
- Format fit: The Whitney release is an explicitly curated greatest‑hits compilation. That directly matches my stated love of greatest‑hits‑style discs and collector‑friendly collections — it packages recognisable, short, singalong tracks in a single, radio‑ready sequence and includes informative liner notes. Those exact attributes are central to my preferences.
