The user updates his self-description as follows: I now gravitate to raw, guitar‑driven American alternative with lo‑fi grit, abrasive but twangy riffs, concise 2–3 minute songs and tight, punchy rhythms. I love analog‑tape warmth and immediacy, emotionally direct (sometimes explicit) lyrics, and unconventional packaging or metadata quirks that reward repeat listens and collector interest. 
