Dislikes: I dislike excessive theatrical/operatic vocal melodrama, organ‑forward bombast, over‑polished radio gloss that smooths grit, ballad‑heavy or vocal‑showcase compilations that kill pace, sprawling instrumental detours, and abrupt grandiose tempo shifts that break momentum.

