The user updates his self-description as follows: I now most strongly gravitate to tight, iconic dance‑pop — syncopated, groove‑first basslines, crisp percussive mixes, layered multi‑instrument arrangements and AOR‑level high‑polish production that reward full‑album listening and repeated plays. I prize irresistible hooks, concise radio‑length tracks, cohesive sequencing with varied tempos, and dynamic vocal delivery that stays in the pocket rather than overpowering the groove.
