Why the lo‑fi American alternative CD fits: 
- Song length and pacing: The lo‑fi set’s concise 2–3‑minute songs directly match my preference for radio‑length, momentum‑preserving tracks that invite repeat plays. 
- Groove and rhythm focus: The description emphasizes tight, syncopated rhythms and punchy arrangements that foreground groove and clarity — exactly the dance‑forward, groove‑first quality I prize. 
